title: 'Serves the purpose'
body: It's light weight and easy to use, holds a surprisingly large amount of stuff. It's helped organise my dresser in a neat way. The only thing I would mention is that there are divisions/partitions along the lengths of the stand inside so, unless your products are small, they will not fit. Adjustable partitions or no partitions at all would've been better. But I'm happy with it because it's affordable & works well.
